<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Travel Destinations</title>

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: aliceblue;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      color: darkblue;
    }

    .place-card {
      background-color: white;
      border: 2px solid steelblue;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      overflow: auto;
    }

    /* Float Property */
    .place-image {
      width: 150px;
      height: 100px;
      background-color: lightblue;
      float: left;
      margin-right: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 100px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: navy;
    }

    .description {
      color: dimgray;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>Famous Travel Destinations</h1>

  <div class="place-card">
    <div class="place-image">Image</div>

    <p class="description">
      Paris is known for its beautiful architecture, famous landmarks,
      and rich cultural history. Millions of tourists visit every year.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="place-card">
    <div class="place-image">Image</div>

    <p class="description">
      Tokyo is a vibrant city that combines modern technology with
      traditional culture, making it a unique destination.
    </p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
